#      Intersection over Union Metrics
def metrix(y_original, y_predict, smooth=1):
    intersection = K.sum(K.abs(y_original * y_predict), axis=[1,2,3])
    union = K.sum(y_original,[1,2,3])+K.sum(y_predict,[1,2,3])-intersection
    IntersectionOverUnion = K.mean((intersection + smooth) / (union + smooth), axis=0)
    return IntersectionOverUnion

#       Soft dice Loss Function
def dice_coef(y_original, y_predict, smooth = 1):
    y_original_flatten = K.flatten(y_original)
    y_predict_flatten = K.flatten(y_predict)
    intersection = K.sum(y_original_flatten * y_predict_flatten)
    return (2. * intersection + smooth) / (K.sum(y_original_flatten) + K.sum(y_predict_flatten) + smooth)

def soft_dice_loss(y_original, y_predict):
    return 1-dice_coef(y_original, y_predict)

# New Created W model

Input_1 = tf.keras.Input(shape=(1024,1024,3))

#      Convolutional layers
cnn_layer_1 = keras.layers.Conv2D(16, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'relu')(Input_1)

cnn_layer_2 = keras.layers.Conv2D(16, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'relu')(cnn_layer_1)

cnn_layer_3 = keras.layers.Conv2D(16, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'relu')(cnn_layer_2)

#      maxpooling
max_pool_1 = keras.layers.MaxPooling2D(pool_size = (2, 2), strides = 2)(cnn_layer_3)

#      Convolutional layers
cnn_layer_4 = keras.layers.Conv2D(32, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'relu')(max_pool_1)

cnn_layer_5 = keras.layers.Conv2D(32, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'relu')(cnn_layer_4)

cnn_layer_6 = keras.layers.Conv2D(32, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'relu')(cnn_layer_5)

#      maxpooling
max_pool_2 = keras.layers.MaxPooling2D(pool_size = (2, 2), strides = 2)(cnn_layer_6)

#      Convolutional layers
cnn_layer_7 = keras.layers.Conv2D(64, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'relu')(max_pool_2)

cnn_layer_8 = keras.layers.Conv2D(64, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'relu')(cnn_layer_7)

cnn_layer_9 = keras.layers.Conv2D(64, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'relu')(cnn_layer_8)

#      upscale
up_scale_1 = concatenate([Conv2DTranspose(32, (2, 2), strides = 2, padding='same')(cnn_layer_9), cnn_layer_6])

#      Convolutional layers
cnn_layer_10 = keras.layers.Conv2D(32, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'relu')(up_scale_1)

cnn_layer_11 = keras.layers.Conv2D(32, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'relu')(cnn_layer_10)

cnn_layer_12 = keras.layers.Conv2D(32, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'relu')(cnn_layer_11)


#     upscale
up_scale_2 = concatenate([Conv2DTranspose(16, (2, 2), strides = 2, padding='same')(cnn_layer_12), cnn_layer_3])


#      Convolutional layers
cnn_layer_13 = keras.layers.Conv2D(16, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'relu')(up_scale_2)

cnn_layer_14 = keras.layers.Conv2D(16, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'relu')(cnn_layer_13)

cnn_layer_15 = keras.layers.Conv2D(16, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'relu')(cnn_layer_14)

#     maxpooling
max_pool_3 = keras.layers.MaxPooling2D(pool_size = (2, 2), strides = 2)(cnn_layer_15)

#      Convolutional layers
cnn_layer_16 = keras.layers.Conv2D(32, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'relu')(max_pool_3)

cnn_layer_17 = keras.layers.Conv2D(32, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'relu')(cnn_layer_16)

cnn_layer_18 = keras.layers.Conv2D(32, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'relu')(cnn_layer_17)

#      maxpooling
max_pool_4 = keras.layers.MaxPooling2D(pool_size = (2, 2), strides = 2)(cnn_layer_18)

#      Convolutional layers
cnn_layer_19 = keras.layers.Conv2D(64, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'relu')(max_pool_4)

cnn_layer_20 = keras.layers.Conv2D(64, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'relu')(cnn_layer_19)

cnn_layer_21 = keras.layers.Conv2D(64, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'relu')(cnn_layer_20)



#     upscale
up_scale_3 = concatenate([Conv2DTranspose(32, (2, 2), strides = 2, padding='same')(cnn_layer_21), cnn_layer_18])


#      Convolutional layers
cnn_layer_22 = keras.layers.Conv2D(32, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'relu')(up_scale_3)

cnn_layer_23 = keras.layers.Conv2D(32, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'relu')(cnn_layer_22)

cnn_layer_24 = keras.layers.Conv2D(32, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'relu')(cnn_layer_23)

#     upscale
up_scale_4 = concatenate([Conv2DTranspose(16, (2, 2), strides = 2, padding='same')(cnn_layer_24), cnn_layer_15])


#      Convolutional layers
cnn_layer_25 = keras.layers.Conv2D(16, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'relu')(up_scale_4)

cnn_layer_26 = keras.layers.Conv2D(16, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'relu')(cnn_layer_25)

cnn_layer_27 = keras.layers.Conv2D(16, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'relu')(cnn_layer_26)

cnn_final = keras.layers.Conv2D(1, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'sigmoid')(cnn_layer_27)


w_model = keras.Model(inputs = Input_1 , outputs = cnn_final)

w_model.summary()

Input_1 = tf.keras.Input(shape=(1024,1024,3))

#      maxpooling

cnn_layer_5 = keras.layers.Conv2D(32, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'relu')(max_pool_1)

cnn_layer_7 = keras.layers.Conv2D(32, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'relu')(cnn_layer_6)

cnn_layer_8 = keras.layers.Conv2D(32, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'relu')(cnn_layer_7)

cnn_final = keras.layers.Conv2D(1, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'sigmoid')(cnn_layer_43)

final_model = keras.Model(inputs = Input_1 , outputs = cnn_final)

# New Created W model

Input_1 = tf.keras.Input(shape=(1024,1024,3))

#      Convolutional layers 1024*1024
cnn_layer_1 = keras.layers.Conv2D(16, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'relu')(Input_1)

cnn_layer_2 = keras.layers.Conv2D(16, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'relu')(cnn_layer_1)

cnn_layer_3 = keras.layers.Conv2D(16, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'relu')(cnn_layer_2)

#      maxpooling
max_pool_1 = keras.layers.MaxPooling2D(pool_size = (2, 2), strides = 2)(cnn_layer_3)

#      Convolutional layers   512 *512
cnn_layer_4 = keras.layers.Conv2D(32, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'relu')(max_pool_1)

cnn_layer_5 = keras.layers.Conv2D(32, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'relu')(cnn_layer_4)

cnn_layer_6 = keras.layers.Conv2D(32, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'relu')(cnn_layer_5)

#      maxpooling
max_pool_2 = keras.layers.MaxPooling2D(pool_size = (2, 2), strides = 2)(cnn_layer_6)

#      Convolutional layers   256*256
cnn_layer_7 = keras.layers.Conv2D(64, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'relu')(max_pool_2)

cnn_layer_8 = keras.layers.Conv2D(64, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'relu')(cnn_layer_7)

cnn_layer_9 = keras.layers.Conv2D(64, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'relu')(cnn_layer_8)

#      maxpooling
max_pool_3 = keras.layers.MaxPooling2D(pool_size = (2, 2), strides = 2)(cnn_layer_9)

#      Convolutional layers   128*128
cnn_layer_10 = keras.layers.Conv2D(128, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'relu')(max_pool_3)

cnn_layer_11 = keras.layers.Conv2D(128, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'relu')(cnn_layer_10)

cnn_layer_12 = keras.layers.Conv2D(128, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'relu')(cnn_layer_11)
print(cnn_layer_12.shape)

#      upscale
up_scale_1 = concatenate([Conv2DTranspose(64, (2, 2), strides = 2, padding='same')(cnn_layer_12), cnn_layer_9])

#      Convolutional layers     256*256
cnn_layer_13 = keras.layers.Conv2D(64, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'relu')(up_scale_1)

cnn_layer_14 = keras.layers.Conv2D(64, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'relu')(cnn_layer_13)

cnn_layer_15 = keras.layers.Conv2D(64, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'relu')(cnn_layer_14)


#     upscale
up_scale_2 = concatenate([Conv2DTranspose(32, (2, 2), strides = 2, padding='same')(cnn_layer_15), cnn_layer_6])


#      Convolutional layers     512*512
cnn_layer_16 = keras.layers.Conv2D(32, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'relu')(up_scale_2)

cnn_layer_17 = keras.layers.Conv2D(32, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'relu')(cnn_layer_16)

cnn_layer_18 = keras.layers.Conv2D(32, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'relu')(cnn_layer_17)


#     maxpooling
max_pool_4 = keras.layers.MaxPooling2D(pool_size = (2, 2), strides = 2)(cnn_layer_18)

#      Convolutional layers      256*256
cnn_layer_19 = keras.layers.Conv2D(64, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'relu')(max_pool_4)

cnn_layer_20 = keras.layers.Conv2D(64, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'relu')(cnn_layer_19)

cnn_layer_21 = keras.layers.Conv2D(64, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'relu')(cnn_layer_20)

#      maxpooling
max_pool_5 = keras.layers.MaxPooling2D(pool_size = (2, 2), strides = 2)(cnn_layer_21)

#      Convolutional layers      128*128
cnn_layer_22 = keras.layers.Conv2D(128, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'relu')(max_pool_5)

cnn_layer_23 = keras.layers.Conv2D(128, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'relu')(cnn_layer_22)

cnn_layer_24 = keras.layers.Conv2D(128, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'relu')(cnn_layer_23)



#     upscale
up_scale_3 = concatenate([Conv2DTranspose(64, (2, 2), strides = 2, padding='same')(cnn_layer_24), cnn_layer_21])


#      Convolutional layers    256*256
cnn_layer_25 = keras.layers.Conv2D(64, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'relu')(up_scale_3)

cnn_layer_26 = keras.layers.Conv2D(64, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'relu')(cnn_layer_25)

cnn_layer_27 = keras.layers.Conv2D(64, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'relu')(cnn_layer_26)


#     upscale
up_scale_4 = concatenate([Conv2DTranspose(32, (2, 2), strides = 2, padding='same')(cnn_layer_27), cnn_layer_18])


#      Convolutional layers     512*512
cnn_layer_28 = keras.layers.Conv2D(32, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'relu')(up_scale_4)

cnn_layer_29 = keras.layers.Conv2D(32, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'relu')(cnn_layer_28)

cnn_layer_30 = keras.layers.Conv2D(32, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'relu')(cnn_layer_29)



#     upscale
up_scale_5 = concatenate([Conv2DTranspose(16, (2, 2), strides = 2, padding='same')(cnn_layer_30), cnn_layer_3])

 
#      Convolutional layers    1024*1024
cnn_layer_31 = keras.layers.Conv2D(16, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'relu')(up_scale_5)

cnn_layer_32 = keras.layers.Conv2D(16, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'relu')(cnn_layer_31)

cnn_layer_33 = keras.layers.Conv2D(16, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'relu')(cnn_layer_32)

cnn_final_layer = keras.layers.Conv2D(1, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'sigmoid')(cnn_layer_33)


double_v_model = keras.Model(inputs = Input_1 , outputs = cnn_final_layer)

Input_1 = tf.keras.Input(shape=(1024,1024,3))

#      Convolutional layers 1024*1024
cnn_layer_1 = keras.layers.Conv2D(16, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'relu')(Input_1)

cnn_layer_2 = keras.layers.Conv2D(16, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'relu')(cnn_layer_1)

cnn_layer_3 = keras.layers.Conv2D(16, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'relu')(cnn_layer_2)

#      maxpooling
max_pool_1 = keras.layers.MaxPooling2D(pool_size = (2, 2), strides = 2)(cnn_layer_3)

#      Convolutional layers   512 *512
cnn_layer_4 = keras.layers.Conv2D(32, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'relu')(max_pool_1)

cnn_layer_5 = keras.layers.Conv2D(32, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'relu')(cnn_layer_4)

cnn_layer_6 = keras.layers.Conv2D(32, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'relu')(cnn_layer_5)

#      maxpooling
max_pool_2 = keras.layers.MaxPooling2D(pool_size = (2, 2), strides = 2)(cnn_layer_6)

#      Convolutional layers   256*256
cnn_layer_7 = keras.layers.Conv2D(64, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'relu')(max_pool_2)

cnn_layer_8 = keras.layers.Conv2D(64, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'relu')(cnn_layer_7)

cnn_layer_9 = keras.layers.Conv2D(64, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'relu')(cnn_layer_8)

#      maxpooling
max_pool_3 = keras.layers.MaxPooling2D(pool_size = (2, 2), strides = 2)(cnn_layer_9)

#      Convolutional layers   128*128
cnn_layer_10 = keras.layers.Conv2D(128, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'relu')(max_pool_3)

cnn_layer_11 = keras.layers.Conv2D(128, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'relu')(cnn_layer_10)

cnn_layer_12 = keras.layers.Conv2D(128, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'relu')(cnn_layer_11)
print(cnn_layer_12.shape)

#      upscale
up_scale_1 = concatenate([Conv2DTranspose(64, (2, 2), strides = 2, padding='same')(cnn_layer_12), cnn_layer_9])

#      Convolutional layers     256*256
cnn_layer_13 = keras.layers.Conv2D(64, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'relu')(up_scale_1)

cnn_layer_14 = keras.layers.Conv2D(64, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'relu')(cnn_layer_13)

cnn_layer_15 = keras.layers.Conv2D(64, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'relu')(cnn_layer_14)

cnn_layer_18 = keras.layers.Conv2D(32, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'relu')(cnn_layer_17)

cnn_layer_22 = concatenate([cnn_layer_12, max_pool_5])

#     upscale
up_scale_5 = concatenate([Conv2DTranspose(16, (2, 2), strides = 2, padding='same')(cnn_layer_30), cnn_layer_3])

 
#      Convolutional layers    1024*1024
cnn_layer_31 = keras.layers.Conv2D(16, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'relu')(up_scale_5)

cnn_layer_33 = keras.layers.Conv2D(16, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'relu')(cnn_layer_32)

final_layer = keras.layers.Conv2D(1, kernel_size = 3, padding = "same",  activation = 'sigmoid')(cnn_layer_33)
